name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: Business identifiers assigned to this care team by the performer or other systems which remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

desc: Business identifiers assigned to this care team by the performer or other systems which remain constant as the resource is updated and propagates from server to server.

name: $status
desc: Returns: Indicates the current state of the care team.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates the current state of the care team.

name: $category
desc: Returns: Identifies what kind of team.  This is to support differentiation between multiple co-existing teams, such as care plan team, episode of care team, longitudinal care team.

name: $addcategory
desc: Identifies what kind of team.  This is to support differentiation between multiple co-existing teams, such as care plan team, episode of care team, longitudinal care team.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Identifies what kind of team.  This is to support differentiation between multiple co-existing teams, such as care plan team, episode of care team, longitudinal care team.

name: $::name
desc: Returns: A label for human use intended to distinguish like teams.  E.g. the "red" vs. "green" trauma teams.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: A label for human use intended to distinguish like teams.  E.g. the "red" vs. "green" trauma teams.

name: $subject
desc: Returns: Identifies the patient or group whose intended care is handled by the team.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Identifies the patient or group whose intended care is handled by the team.

name: $encounter
desc: Returns: The Encounter during which this CareTeam was created or to which the creation of this record is tightly associated.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The Encounter during which this CareTeam was created or to which the creation of this record is tightly associated.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Indicates when the team did (or is intended to) come into effect and end.
